Reviews:
meine yehee maximus ki hid do baar pehlay khareedi hui hain, aur kasam se, dono ka experience bohat hee acha tha. bohat tez aur mazedar hids theen yeh aur aisi tez hid lights to meine dekhee bhee nai pehlay.

choaty se gaoun se taluq hai mera, yaha jo bhee hid hotee hain, 400 watt ki keh kar bechte hain , lekin hotee kuch 20 watt ki hain, lekin yeh maximus ki waqai mein 200 watt ki lagtee hai kiunkay bohat bright hai yeh. mera car modification ka kaam hai aur meray customers ko yeh hid bohat pasand hai. mashaallah se thoray se customers ne request kee hai inko yehee wali hid chayiey.

sath mein 6 maheenay ki warranty bhee hai, jo meine inko dee hui hai aur unki taraf se bhee kissi tarhan ki complain nai ayee. 6000 lumen hain ismein tou light kuch zyada hee blinding aur tez hai aur issi light ka hee sahee maza hai jab road pe lekay ghumein :d

Reviews:
meine yeh baby washer bachon kay kapron kay liay khareeda hai. waisay tou machine hai, lekin mujhe pataya gaya tha kay gaba bohat acha brand hai aur sath mein warranty bhee derahay hain tou meine order kardia.

mil bhee gaya jaldi aur kaam bhee bohat acha krraha hai. baby washer aur spinner baby kay kapron ko dhonay kay liay bohata chee hai, aur akbhee kabar tou baroun kay joray bhee dhul jatay hain, lekin kuch 3 4 joray kiunkay ismein baray kaproun ki itnee jaga nai hai. iska size bhee munasib hai aur isko chalana bhee abra asan hai, aik average machine ki tarhan hee kaam krtee hai.

mein tou samajh rahee thee kay agar umeedon kay mutabiq nai aaya , tou wapis karadoongi, lekin abhee tak jitna istemal kia hai, mein isse razi hoon. bohat shukarya aapka, is genuine product kay liay :)
